					</div>
					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">‚úÖ</div>
						<h3>On-device by default</h3>
						<p>Your data stays on your phone. No bank accounts, no account linking.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">üßæ</div>
