				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Free</h2>
					<p>Kontana is a free, device-based app. Join the waitlist to be notified at launch.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="pricing-grid">
					<div class="pricing-card">
						<h3>Free at launch</h3>
						<div class="price">$0</div>
						<ul class="pricing-features">
							<li>‚úì On-device cash log</li>
							<li>‚úì Categories and notes</li>
							<li>‚úì Offline-first</li>
							<li>‚úì Optional exports</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="#waitlist" class="btn btn-outline">Join waitlist</a>
					</div>
					<div class="pricing-card featured">
						<div class="pricing-badge">Privacy-first</div>
						<h3>No bank linking</h3>
						<div class="price">Cash-only</div>
