							<li>‚úì Built with privacy in mind</li>
							<li>‚úì Feedback shapes the roadmap</li>
							<li>‚úì Early access for contributors</li>
							<li>‚úì Transparent development</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="#waitlist" class="btn btn-outline">Join waitlist</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="faq" class="faq">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>FAQ</h2>
					<p>Questions we get from privacy-first cash users.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-grid">
					<details class="faq-item">
						<summary>Do I need to link a bank account?</summary>
						<div class="faq-body">No. Kontana is cash-only by design. You can use it without linking any accounts.</div>
					</details>
					<details class="faq-item">
						<summary>Is my data stored in the cloud?</summary>
						<div class="faq-body">The goal is privacy-first, on-device storage. You‚Äôll stay in control of what leaves your device.</div>
					</details>
					<details class="faq-item">
						<summary>Why use cash at all?</summary>
						<div class="faq-body">Many people find cash helps reduce impulse spending, improves awareness, and increases privacy. Kontana is designed for that lifestyle.</div>
					</details>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="waitlist" class="cta">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="cta-content">
					<h2>Get notified when Kontana launches</h2>
					<p>Want a free, on-device cash tracker that helps you rely less on banks? Join the waitlist and we'll email you when it's ready.</p>
					<form id="waitlist-form">
						<input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
						<div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="0x4AAAAAACXPTpqdso7QmAhX"></div>
